text: The Southern Ports Highway is a rural highway in South Australia that connects Kingston SE with Millicent via Rendelsham, Southend, Beachport and Robe. The Southern Ports Highway is the green route along the coast near the bottom right ==Major intersections== ==See also== * Highways in Australia * List of highways in South Australia ==References== ==External links== *Southern Ports Highway webpage on Ozroads website Category:Highways in Australia Category:Roads in South Australia
